t; In this field we define the fixed wholesale price of the item which is without VAT. We know this by the checkbox&amp;nbsp;that is not checked. If the customer is wholesaler, in customer pricing the items will automatically have the wholesale price.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=&quot;kle&quot;&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Retail Price :&lt;/STRONG&gt; In this field we define the fixed retail price of the item which is with VAT. We know this by the checkbox&amp;nbsp;that&amp;nbsp;is checked. If the customer is retail, in customer pricing the items will automatically have the retail price.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=&quot;kle&quot;&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;VAT Category :&lt;/STRONG&gt; Here you define the VAT category for this type.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=&quot;kle&quot;&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Unit of Measurement:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;In this field you define the measurement unit of this item&amp;nbsp;(exmp. Piece, Kilos, Meters etc.)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=&quot;kle&quot;&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;Traffic (This tab is shown only on edit and view item window)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=&quot;kle&quot;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Remaining : &lt;/STRONG&gt;This field will display the remaining of this item on your storage.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/P&gt;            &lt;/body&gt;    &lt;/html&gt;" prefHeight="442.0" prefWidth="685.0" BorderPane.alignment="CENTER">
